name: Dishes
description: At Vegan Halmstad you can be rest assured that you are getting top of the line vegan dishes prepared by some of the finest chef in the city. What make us stand out is that all our ingredient source from local organic farmers. Vegan Halmstad dishes have been rated best in Sweden for the past three consecutive year by vegan association of Sweden. While we are proud of achivements so far, we continue to innovate to keep making your experience with us better

products.name: Lentil stew
products.description: vegan stew with lots of flavor! Potatoes, carrots and red lentils are seasoned in the stew with ginger, turmeric and chili.

products.name: Carot soup
products.description: White beans and roasted carrots with garlic are mixed into a creamy soup.Top with olive oil and pumpkin seeds.White beans and roasted carrots with garlic are mixed into a creamy soup.Top with olive oil and pumpkin seeds.

products.name: Peanut stew with cauliflower
products.description: Vegan stew with a lot of flavor! The cauliflower is boiled with peanut butter, ginger, lime and sriracha. Serve with Asian coleslaw.

products.name: potato and beans soup
products.description: Boiled potatoes and white beans are mixed into a creamy soup together with spices. Drizzle ready-made pesto over and serve with toast.
